data.description: Multiple Offers Received.  Please submit your best offer by 5pm on 1/6/24. Price adjusted on this Charming home with great potential with just a little TLC.  Home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, two car garage, fireplace and a spacious backyard.  You'll love the open floor plan and floor layout.  With just a little work, this home will be gorgeous.   Conveniently located near major highways and near Kirby Park. Solar Panels and storage sheds in backyard included.  Make an offer, seller is negotiable.
